            <bug_when>2009-10-01 15:47:12 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>To modify the the URIs where script files are loaded, the best place seems the 
qx.$$loader.decodeUris method, as it is both used in the loader itself (to load 
the boot part), as well as later in the qx.io2.PartLoader (which simply links 
to this method under the same name).

This will allow unified modification of script URIs, in a dynamic way when the 
application is loading in the browser.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
