            <thetext>New config options

   compile-source/decode-uris-plug
   compile-dist/code/decode-uris-plug

allow you to specify a file path to a JS file. The contents of this file will 
be spliced into the qx.$$loader.decodeUris() method, just before the end of the 
loop that expands all input id&#39;s. In the JS code, you can modify the variable 
&quot;euri&quot;, which will contain the current script URI.

With r20253.</thetext>
